  "events": [],
  "notes": "Third floor of the Olivine Lighthouse. Has three trainers: Sailor Terrell (1 Poliwhirl Lv20), Gentleman Preston (2x Growlithe Lv18 — confirms Jasmine used to use Rock types), and Bird Keeper Theo (5x Pidgey, uses SPRITE_YOUNGSTER in ASM). One item ball: Ether. This floor has the most staircases of any floor — 9 warp events total — reflecting the complex hole-riddled layout requiring multiple paths to navigate between east and west sections. Theo's after-battle dialogue indicates the route to the upper floors is not obvious even for trainers on this floor. Preston's after-battle dialogue is key Jasmine lore: she used to use Rock types (Onix) before switching to Steel."
